{"sn11.8:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 11.8 ","sn11.8:0.2":"1. Pathamavagga ","sn11.8:0.3":"Verocanaasurindasutta ","sn11.8:1.1":"Savatthiyam jetavane. ","sn11.8:1.2":"Tena kho pana samayena bhagava divaviharagato hoti patisallino. ","sn11.8:1.3":"Atha kho sakko ca devanamindo verocano ca asurindo yena bhagava tenupasankamimsu; upasankamitva paccekam dvarabaham nissaya atthamsu. ","sn11.8:1.4":"Atha kho verocano asurindo bhagavato santike imam gatham abhasi: ","sn11.8:2.1":"“Vayametheva puriso, ","sn11.8:2.2":"yava atthassa nipphada; ","sn11.8:2.3":"Nipphannasobhano attho, ","sn11.8:2.4":"verocanavaco idan”ti. ","sn11.8:3.1":"“Vayametheva puriso, ","sn11.8:3.2":"yava atthassa nipphada; ","sn11.8:3.3":"Nipphannasobhano attho, ","sn11.8:3.4":"khantya bhiyyo na vijjati”ti. ","sn11.8:4.1":"“Sabbe satta atthajata, ","sn11.8:4.2":"tattha tattha yatharaham; ","sn11.8:4.3":"Samyogaparama tveva, ","sn11.8:4.4":"sambhoga sabbapaninam; ","sn11.8:4.5":"Nipphannasobhano attho, ","sn11.8:4.6":"verocanavaco idan”ti. ","sn11.8:5.1":"“Sabbe satta atthajata, ","sn11.8:5.2":"tattha tattha yatharaham; ","sn11.8:5.3":"Samyogaparama tveva, ","sn11.8:5.4":"sambhoga sabbapaninam; ","sn11.8:5.5":"Nipphannasobhano attho, ","sn11.8:5.6":"khantya bhiyyo na vijjati”ti. "}